---
title: Speedy Salmon and Cranberry-Apple Chutney with Roasted Potatoes and Feta Crumble
description: Elevate your salmon dinner with a quick apple and cranberry relish! Completing this mid-winter stunner, we have feta-sprinkled roasted potatoes and a deliciously understated vinaigrette-dressed salad.
